所以最痛苦係飲唔醉，永遠都好清醒自己做緊乜，但一樣會劏會嘔同傷胃。<br />\n<br />\n我試過扮醉，但冇用，越扮覺得自己越on9.<br />\n明知on9 都去做醒返就越痛苦。"},{"pid":"98c51af9692606be8730411932c3218c7855163c","tid":1105663,"uid":209120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T02:55:24.000Z","msg":"戒酒啦各位,飲酒又冇益又解決唔到問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75d7a747fc92252d6ac7c096529eddd86cb520f7","tid":1105663,"uid":45431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T02:56:18.000Z","msg":"鐘意飲但唔鐘意醉又點睇?"},{"pid":"6ee3e2cdc3fda353d92d269b61f7dea4a984b1f5","tid":1105663,"uid":77643,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T03:12:50.000Z","msg":"身邊冇人關心自己，唯有靠飲酒先至搵到一絲心靈上嘅安慰<br />\n<br />\n最近都隊酒隊得幾密，不過搵唔到替代方法去釋放自己"},{"pid":"204bbfdab199e1c838c95a0f14286c26728e80c3","tid":1105663,"uid":209120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ee3e2cdc3fda353d92d269b61f7dea4a984b1f5","tid":1105663,"uid":77643,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T03:12:50.000Z","msg":"身邊冇人關心自己，唯有靠飲酒先至搵到一絲心靈上嘅安慰<br />\n<br />\n最近都隊酒隊得幾密，不過搵唔到替代方法去釋放自己"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T03:20:12.000Z","msg":"好傷㗎,又會嘔到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e58ddad701f942ea82c5b6da274e08ff148b3566","tid":1105663,"uid":209120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75d7a747fc92252d6ac7c096529eddd86cb520f7","tid":1105663,"uid":45431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T02:56:18.000Z","msg":"鐘意飲但唔鐘意醉又點睇?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T03:32:33.000Z","msg":"講多啲"},{"pid":"d5ade42488b92a0e92e934f8c848aeeb97814bc4","tid":1105663,"uid":77643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"204bbfdab199e1c838c95a0f14286c26728e80c3","tid":1105663,"uid":209120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ee3e2cdc3fda353d92d269b61f7dea4a984b1f5","tid":1105663,"uid":77643,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T03:12:50.000Z","msg":"身邊